title: Oversized Closets, Garages, Washer & Dryer Connections
posting_body: ['The Landing at Mansfield Apartments is the apartment you’ve been looking for in Mansfield, Texas.', 'With comfortable one-, two-, and three-bedroom homes complete with washers and dryers, private patios, and kitchen pantries, you’re guaranteed to find a place to live with a lifestyle to love.', 'What’s more, as a member of the community you’ll also have access to our outdoor grilling stations and resort-style swimming pool, all conveniently located near shopping and dining at Mansfield Towne Crossing.', 'Find a home at The Landing at Mansfield Apartments, where living more is the new standard.', '-Smart Home Technology', '-Oversized Closets', '-Luxer One Package Lockers', '-Washer and Dryer', '-Brush Nickel Finishes', '-Valet Waste Services', '-Rapid-Response Maintenance', '-Close to Public Transit', '-Walkable to Shops & Dining at Mansfield Towne Crossing', '-Internet Cafe', '-Hot', 'Tub', '-Vaulted Ceilings', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Pricing and availability subject to change.', 'Equal housing opportunity.']
